---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure & Methodology" description="HostHive affiliate disclosure and review methodology.">
  <article class="legal-page">
    <span class="page-label">Methodology</span>
    <h1>How we test,<br/><em>and how we earn.</em></h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <section>
      <h2>How We Earn Revenue</h2>
      <p>HostHive participates in affiliate programs with Bluehost, SiteGround, Hostinger, Cloudways, WP Engine, Kinsta, and other hosting providers. We earn commissions when you purchase through our links at no extra cost to you.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Editorial Independence</h2>
      <p>Commissions never influence reviews or ratings. Our team tests every provider independently. We include both pros and cons in every review. Companies cannot pay for higher scores or placement.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Our Testing Process</h2>
      <p>Every host undergoes uptime monitoring, speed benchmarking, support evaluation, and feature analysis. We re-test regularly to keep reviews current. Scores reflect real-world performance, not marketing claims.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>Email <a href="mailto:info@host-hive.net">info@host-hive.net</a>.</p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page { max-width: var(--max-width); margin: 0 auto; padding: var(--space-3xl) 0; }
  .page-label { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--ink-400); display: block; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }
  .legal-page h1 { margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }
  .legal-page h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--ink-500); }
  .updated { color: var(--ink-400); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl); }
  .legal-page section { margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl); }
  .legal-page h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-md); margin-top: 0; }
  .legal-page p { color: var(--ink-700); line-height: 1.8; }
  .legal-page a { color: var(--violet); }
  .legal-page a:hover { color: var(--violet-hover); }
</style>
